const body = "\n\n\n## Introduction\n\n“Grocery at your doorstep”– the biggest boon in the time of the coronavirus crisis. Who doesn’t enjoy doorstep delivery rather than standing in long queues? If you run any kind of grocery outlet, now is the perfect time to go online! Online grocery businesses have a high chance of success owing because :\n\n  \n- <strong>Time is everything</strong>\n\nOne can choose to stay at home and still have a shelf full of groceries. No one likes to stand in a long queue or travel to the end of the city to get their favorite veggies.\n\n- <strong>Deals! Deals Deals!</strong>\n\nCustomers are more attracted by the deals and offers given by the online platforms. They are always willing to avail of discounts, vouchers, coupons, etc for additional savings.\n\n- <strong>Ease of use</strong>\n\nUsers can order at the comfort of your home, select the items, add them incart and have them delivered at your doorstep.\n\n- <strong>Array of products</strong>\n\nDeliver a rich variety and categories of grocery products to your customers.\n\n- <strong>Personalized shopping experience</strong>\n\nUnderstand your customer’s demand and organize your business model accordingly.\n\n\n### Must-have features for your own online grocery platform\nAny guesses? What features will be helpful for the online grocery business? Here are some features that are a must for a grocery delivery platform:\n\n#### Website and mobile platforms\nAn attractive and responsive online presence to elevate your customer experience.\n\n#### Digital menu\nBuild an updated online ordering menu. Easily add or delete product categories through the catalogue management feature\n\n#### Real time tracking\nWith the help of GPS tracking, track your delivery agents on a real time basis.\n\n#### Push Notifications\nTake a wise approach for push notifications. Use them to inform your customers of updates like : ride started, on the way, and etc.\n\n#### Social Media integration\nBecause why not! Engage with your customers and increase your brand reach and awareness for improved user experience.\n\n#### Seamless gateways\nA one page checkout to display all elements of a standard checkout including basket contains, shipping address and secured payment option.\n\n#### Automate your services\nLead a step ahead from competitors with services like exclusive subscriptions, kiosks, and sensor-based payment\n\n#### Scheduled Ordering\nBecause why not! Engage with your customers and increase your brand reach and awareness for improved user experience.\n\nStop Thinking, Start Acting!\n\n[Request For Free Consultation](/contact-us)\n\nStop worrying too much, if you are thinking of grocery delivery app development then this is the right place. The demand is very high and availability is all that matters. Invest in a tried and tested grocery delivery app development with us.\n\nNestorbird is a digital solution company that is currently catering to various grocery delivery software with the best built-in features. Be ready to create a grocery delivery app for your profitable business! Check out our app features.";
